    - Inter-operable
        - Win, AIX, Linux, Pi, macOS
        - Code can be used across platforms without conversion
        - Data files can be used across 32/64 bit, Unicode vs Classic, Big- vs Little-Endian
            - Even if transmitted via TCP sockets
    
